{"title":"党的孩子最听党的话","authors":["红小兵儿歌创作组"],"dates":[{"year":1974,"month":10,"day":11}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"党的孩子最听党的话"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京西四北小学"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红小兵儿歌创作组"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"庄严党旗下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈入党啦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬子也举手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心里乐开花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“妈妈是党的人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是党的孩子呀。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从今跟着党，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刀山火海也不怕。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人烧死了妈妈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烧不尽革命的根芽。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“映山红”遍山开红花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬子在斗争中长大。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"机警通过敌哨卡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为游击队送盐巴。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲手杀死胡汉三，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为咱穷人报仇啦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪闪红星头上戴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一支钢枪肩上挎。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬子参军跟着党，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"消灭蒋匪打天下。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红小兵是党的孩子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红小兵是革命的根芽。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们要学潘冬子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"继续革命大步跨。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":3,"page_end":3}